<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>고객센터 답글 작성</title>
    <style>
        /* 전체 기본 스타일 초기화 */
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* 상단 헤더 & 네비게이션 바 */
        .header-bar {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .header-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .logo-area h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #111;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .menu-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .menu-links a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .menu-links a:hover {
            color: #004499;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* 메인 컨텐츠 영역 */
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .board-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
            padding-left: 10px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .info-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #eee;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        /* 입력 폼 양식 스타일 */
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            outline: none;
            font-family: inherit;
            background-color: #fff;
            transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: #0066cc;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
        }

        textarea.form-control {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 200px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* 버튼 영역 */
        .form-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            flex: 2;
            background-color: #111111;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background-color: #2b2b2b;
        }

        .btn-cancel {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #f1f3f5;
            color: #495057;
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
        }

        .btn-cancel:hover {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header-bar">
        <div class="header-container">
            <div class="logo-area">
                <a href="/" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                    <h1>💻 내 쇼핑몰</h1>
                </a>
                <div class="menu-links">
                    <a href="/">상품목록</a>
                    <a href="/cart">장바구니</a>
                    <a href="/board">고객센터</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="board-card">
            <h2 class="section-title">✍️ 답글 작성</h2>
            <div class="info-text">선택하신 문의글에 대한 답변을 명확하게 작성해 주세요.</div>

            <hr>

            <form method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="title">답글 제목</label>

                    <input type="text" id="title" name="title" class="form-control" placeholder="답글 제목을 입력하세요" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="content">내용</label>

                    <textarea id="content" name="content" class="form-control" placeholder="답변 내용을 상세하게 입력해 주세요." required></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-actions">
                    <a href="/board" class="btn btn-cancel">취소</a>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-submit">답글 등록</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>